## Customization

| What | Where | How |
|------|-------|-----|
| Change model | `dags/pdf_research_pipeline.py` | Update `MODEL` constant |
| Process more chunks | `summarize_chunks` task | Change `chunks[:20]` limit |
| Use hi-res OCR | `parse_and_chunk` task | Change `strategy="fast"` → `"hi_res"` |
| Add vector store | After `save_output` | Add a new task using chromadb |

